WEBVTT

00:44:00.000 --> 00:44:05.200
Talk on Evening Program before Sahasrara Puja, Cabella Ligure, May 3rd, 1996

00:44:05.300 --> 00:44:10.100
It has been such a great pleasure

00:44:10.800 --> 00:44:15.800
and glorification of Sahaja Yoga today,

00:44:17.200 --> 00:44:23.700
I remember the day when it started,

00:44:24.200 --> 00:44:28.200
on the 5th May 1970.

00:44:28.800 --> 00:44:32.800
And today I see all of you so much

00:44:33.000 --> 00:44:40.200
engulfed in the Divine love and Divine power.

00:44:42.800 --> 00:44:47.600
The whole thing shows one very great,

00:44:47.700 --> 00:44:51.100
fundamental thing, of Sahasrara:

00:44:51.200 --> 00:44:59.000
that people from so many countries integrated together. Integrated.

00:44:59.800 --> 00:45:04.100
It was Sahaj, spontaneous, but every way

00:45:04.200 --> 00:45:11.100
and there was no confusion, there’s no quarrelling, no fighting, nothing.

00:45:11.200 --> 00:45:14.800
Such an integration, spontaneous,

00:45:14.900 --> 00:45:19.900
whether it is on the stage or stage of life.

00:45:20.000 --> 00:45:25.300
Now, as we are all global personalities,

00:45:25.400 --> 00:45:29.900
we are all integrated and those who were acting

00:45:30.000 --> 00:45:37.500
were enjoying as well as the ones who were looking at them were also enjoying in the same manner.

00:45:38.100 --> 00:45:45.300
It was such a good also integration between the one who was acting,

00:45:45.400 --> 00:45:50.500
or the all those who were there, and all those who were watching –

00:45:50.600 --> 00:45:57.600
I couldn’t understand whether the people who are seeing them are also acting,

00:45:57.700 --> 00:46:02.300
or also those who are acting are also seeing.

00:46:02.400 --> 00:46:05.500
It was a beautiful blending I must say,

00:46:05.600 --> 00:46:09.600
and I congratulate all the leaders of all these five countries,

00:46:09.700 --> 00:46:15.500
who have contributed so well to this deep sense of integration.

00:46:16.100 --> 00:46:19.500
Not that is the integration within that is important

00:46:19.600 --> 00:46:24.800
– of course that’s very important for a personality, but for our work,

00:46:24.900 --> 00:46:30.500
for our global emancipation we need integration of all the nations,

00:46:30.600 --> 00:46:33.800
and understanding of all the nations,

00:46:33.900 --> 00:46:39.400
because these barriers are created by human beings, not by God Almighty.

00:46:39.500 --> 00:46:42.200
So we have transcended those barriers,

00:46:42.300 --> 00:46:48.100
and the way we are all sitting together in a complete integrated mood is –

00:46:48.200 --> 00:46:52.100
you don’t know what your Mother feels, I, I just can’t believe

00:46:52.200 --> 00:46:55.500
that in such a short time this we have achieved,

00:46:55.600 --> 00:46:59.300
in My lifetime I can see all these things happening.

00:46:59.400 --> 00:47:03.400
So it was such a beautiful

00:47:03.500 --> 00:47:09.400
Sahaja, spontaneous, creation of the Spirit of this integration,

00:47:09.500 --> 00:47:12.300
and I congratulate all the leaders for this,

00:47:12.400 --> 00:47:17.200
and we all should thank them, for giving us this beautiful

00:47:17.300 --> 00:47:20.900
integrated, Sahaj-spontaneous

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:25.500
illustration of Sahaj character.

00:47:25.600 --> 00:47:29.600
Thank you very much. May God bless you all.
